      • toPrimitiveArray

        public double[] toPrimitiveArray()
        Description copied from class: AbstractOptionValueList
        Returns array containing values, using primitive element type if possible.

        If AbstractOptionValueList.elementType() is a primitive wrapper type (e.g. Double), this will return an array of the corresponding primitive. Otherwise this is the same as AbstractOptionValueList.toArray().
